---
/* ============================================================
   The margin rule.
   The single red vertical line of ruled ledger / answer paper —
   the margin down the left edge. Static and quiet: it belongs to
   the paper, it isn't a "feature." Pairs with the faint blue
   horizontal rules set on <body> in global.css.

   Removable: delete this file + the <Thread/> include in
   Base.astro and only the red margin disappears.
   ============================================================ */
---

<span class="margin-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>

<style>
  .margin-rule {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    left: clamp(16px, 5vw, 56px);
    width: 1.5px;
    background: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.65;
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .margin-rule { left: 12px; }
  }
</style>
